Package com.example.project

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DataBaseHelper
    This class implements the DataBase of the application and all of the possible operations that you can do with the DataBase
    FopdtParametersActivity
    This class implements the Activity of the Fopdt Server and shows every parameters that you can change
    FopParametersActivity
    This class implements the Activity of the Fop Server and shows every parameters that you can change
    Graphics
    This class is the responsable of getting the data of the database and show in the graphic the values that "U" and "Y" have taken in the last simulation
    MainActivity
    This class implements the Main Activity and shows the two differents kinds of users that you can be (Regulator or Process)
    MyAsyncTaskClientPi
    This class implements the AsyncTask of the Pi client and it makes the connection between the client and the server
    MyAsyncTaskClientPid
    This class implements the AsyncTask of the client Pid and it makes the connection between the client and the server
    MyAsynTaskServerFop
    This class implements the AsyncTask of the Server Fop and it makes the connection between the client and the server
    MyAsynTaskServerFopdt
    This class implements the AsyncTask of the Server Fopdt and it makes the connection between the client and the server
    MyAsynTaskServerSop
    This class implements the AsyncTask of the Server Sop and it makes the connection between the client and the server
    PidParametersActivity
    This class implements the Activity of the Pid client and shows every parameters that you can change
    PiParametersActivity
    This class implements the Activity of the Pi client and shows every parameters that you can change
    PopUpAdvanceOptionsProcess  
    PopUpAdvanceOptionsRegulator  
    ProcessActivity
    This class implements the Process Activity and shows the three differents kinds of Regulator that you can choose (Fop, Fopdt or Sop)
    RegulatorActivity
    This class implements the Regulator Activity and shows the two differents kinds of Regulator that you can choose (Pi or Pid) and a TextField where you have to write the ServerIP
    SopParametersActivity
    This class implements the Activity of the Sop Server and shows every parameters that you can change
